{
  "stem": "21731.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyway, she decided to come in a few days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She took a holiday, or a holiday, or a few days off, and came to Lvov to have a look at this.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, again, I think my husband fell in love with my mother and she with him, because they really-- there was-- it was incredible how close they were; later, how they-- they matched so well together.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, naturally, the engagement was announced.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Parties were held-- engagement party, invitations, this and that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother went back to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And now there was a little, I think you call it hiccup-- 'hi-cup', or hiccup, or what-- because I was a ward of court, because I had no father.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my grandfather died.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My grandfather was my--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--my guardian.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was dead, so the court had to give the permission for me to marry abroad, because perhaps my mother sold me abroad to somebody.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was asked terribly silly questions like, who was Gerte, or what was the name of the Kaiser who died in 1918, I think, or things like that.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they knew that I wasn't a real idiot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was allowed to-- to marry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I got the permission from them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there were now the Parnus family started to get busy, because they couldn't stand that their niece wouldn't have a wonderful trousseau.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother couldn't have afford to buy me, really the-- she could afford only the most important things, say.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the Parnus family in Lvov decided to give me a trousseau that the Schutzes will talk about.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I got-- I don't know how many dozens of this and how many dozens of that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was taken to a dressmaker.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never had before a dress made by a dressmaker.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
